## Secrets & Configurations (CRITICAL)
# Ignore local secrets and connection strings
appsettings.Development.json
appsettings.Local.json
*.usersecrets

# If you use the dotnet user-secrets tool, the actual secrets 
# are stored in your local user profile, which is safe from Git. 
# However, avoid committing any manual override files.

